description:
Brook and Pedro head out in a submersible to infiltrate Big Mom`s stronghold! Meanwhile Luffy, Nami, Chopper and Carrot head into the island chasing the image of Sanji, only to be distracted by the endless supply of sweets and a second Luffy!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Mysterious Forest Full of Candies! Luffy vs. Luffy?!
Ein mysteriöser Wald voller Süßigkeiten! – Ruffy gegen Ruffy!
Okashi na Mori: Luffy tai Luffy!?
Une forêt remplie de sucreries - Luffy contre Luffy !
غابة غامضة مليئة بالحلويات لوفي ضدّ لوفي!؟
お菓子な森 ルフィVS[たい]ルフィ!?
